content: Stanford Court is an urban setting distinctly San Francisco ideal for wedding brunches, rehearsal dinners and all manner of celebration any time of day. Event Spaces can accommodate up to 60-70 guests. Our seasoned culinary team can create custom menus for any event. Stanford Court also provides preferred rates for guests planning to stay over to enjoy all the planned festivities, please contact our Sales team at sales@stanfordcourt.com for more information.
